  "enterpriseForm.toast.failDesc": "There was an error submitting your inquiry. Please try again or contact us directly.",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.failTitle": "Submission Failed",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.rateLimitClientDesc": "Please wait before submitting another form.",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.rateLimitClientTitle": "Too many requests",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.rateLimitServerDesc": "You've submitted too many forms. Please try again later.",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.rateLimitServerTitle": "Limit reached",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.successDesc": "Thank you for your interest! Our enterprise team will contact you within 24 hours.",
  "enterpriseForm.toast.successTitle": "Enterprise Inquiry Submitted",
  "faq.adv.a1": "Professional and Enterprise plans support multiple calendars, so you can manage more than one location or team member from a single dashboard.",
  "faq.adv.a2": "Yes. Professional and Enterprise plans include analytics on your bookings, so you can see how your schedule is performing.",
  "faq.adv.q1": "Can it manage multiple locations?",
  "faq.adv.q2": "Are analytics available?",
  "faq.adv.title": "Advanced Features",
  "faq.feat.a1": "Yes. Customers can reschedule or cancel their appointments themselves via WhatsApp. The assistant checks new availability automatically and follows the cancellation rules you set.",
  "faq.feat.a2": "Yes. The platform can send automatic appointment reminders by email, and you control when they go out, so customers are less likely to forget their appointment.",
  "faq.feat.a3": "Yes. You can ask customers to pay a deposit or prepay when they book, securely through Stripe. It's optional and you set it per service.",
  "faq.feat.a4": "Yes. Automatic reminders keep the appointment top of mind for your customers, which helps reduce no-shows.",
  "faq.feat.a5": "Absolutely. You can set different services, each with their own price and duration, and the assistant guides customers to the right one.",
  "faq.feat.q1": "Can it reschedule and cancel appointments?",
  "faq.feat.q2": "Does it send reminders?",
  "faq.feat.q3": "Can it process payments?",
  "faq.feat.q4": "Does it help reduce no-shows?",
  "faq.feat.q5": "Can I offer multiple services?",
  "faq.feat.title": "Features",
  "faq.gen.a1": "Our platform is an AI-powered WhatsApp assistant that automatically books, confirms and manages appointments for service-oriented businesses. Customers can make appointments 24/7 via WhatsApp without any manual intervention from you.",
  "faq.gen.a2": "Customers send a WhatsApp message to your business number. Our AI understands their request, checks your availability, automatically books the appointment and sends confirmations to both parties. Everything is kept in sync with your calendar.",
  "faq.gen.a3": "Perfect for hairdressers, dentists, physiotherapists, beauty salons, fitness studios, consultants, lawyers, massage therapists, nail studios, barbershops and all other service providers who work with appointments.",
  "faq.gen.a4": "It takes the back-and-forth of phone calls and manual scheduling off your plate. Instead of answering booking requests yourself, you can focus on your customers while the assistant handles the appointments.",
  "faq.gen.a5": "No. Setup usually takes just a few minutes. You connect the WhatsApp number, set up your calendar and add your services and prices, and the assistant is ready to start booking.",
  "faq.gen.q1": "What is your WhatsApp booking platform?",
  "faq.gen.q2": "How does it work exactly?",
  "faq.gen.q3": "For which types of businesses is this suitable?",
  "faq.gen.q4": "How much time does this save me?",
  "faq.gen.q5": "Is it difficult to set up?",
  "faq.gen.title": "General Questions",
  "faq.hero.badge": "Get Instant Answers",
  "faq.hero.subtitle1": "Everything you need to know about our AI-powered WhatsApp booking platform.",
  "faq.hero.subtitle2": ".",
  "faq.hero.subtitleAccent": "Can't find what you're looking for? Contact our support team",
  "faq.hero.titleLine1": "Frequently Asked ",
  "faq.hero.titleLine2": "Questions",
  "faq.noResults.body": "Try a different search term or view all FAQs below.",
  "faq.noResults.button": "Show all FAQs",
  "faq.noResults.title": "No results found",
  "faq.price.a1": "We offer a free plan, Starter at €30/month, Professional at €60/month, and Enterprise from €300/month. Starter and Professional come with a free 30-day trial and no credit card is required. Enterprise is tailored to your needs, so it doesn't include a free trial.",
  "faq.price.a2": "No setup costs. You only pay the monthly subscription.",
  "faq.price.a3": "Yes, you can switch to a different plan. Changes take effect from your next billing period, so just let us know when you'd like to move up or down.",
  "faq.price.a4": "You can cancel anytime and export your data. If you decide to come back later, just reach out and we'll help you pick up where you left off.",
  "faq.price.a5": "No, you can cancel monthly. And if you pay annually you get a 20% discount.",
  "faq.price.q1": "What does it cost?",
  "faq.price.q2": "Are there setup costs?",
  "faq.price.q3": "Can I upgrade or downgrade?",
  "faq.price.q4": "What happens if I stop?",
  "faq.price.q5": "Is there a long-term contract?",
  "faq.price.title": "Pricing & Plans",
  "faq.search.placeholder": "Search frequently asked questions...",
  "faq.search.popularHeading": "Popular questions:",
  "faq.search.resultsFound": "{{count}} results found",
  "faq.support.a1": "You can reach us by email, and there's a built-in chatbot for quick questions. Professional and Enterprise plans get priority support.",
  "faq.support.a2": "We aim to reply quickly, usually within one business day, and faster for customers on higher plans.",
  "faq.support.a3": "Yes. We provide onboarding guides to help you get set up, and Enterprise customers get hands-on help.",
  "faq.support.a4": "For Enterprise customers we offer a done-for-you setup. Other plans have step-by-step guides and support to make setup easy.",
  "faq.support.q1": "What type of support can I get?",
  "faq.support.q2": "How quickly do I get a response?",
  "faq.support.q3": "Is training available?",
  "faq.support.q4": "Can your team set it up for me?",
  "faq.support.title": "Support",
  "faq.tech.a1": "Yes. We provide a professional WhatsApp Business number and a complete calendar system, so you can get started without needing any extra tools.",
  "faq.tech.a2": "Yes. The assistant works in Dutch and English, and can handle conversations in several other languages too. We're expanding language support over time.",
  "faq.tech.a3": "You stay in control. You're notified of every booked appointment and can review, change or cancel any appointment from your dashboard at any time.",
  "faq.tech.a4": "Yes. We are GDPR compliant, your data is stored securely on European servers, and we never sell your customer data. You can read exactly how we handle data in our Privacy Policy.",
  "faq.tech.a5": "Yes. You set your own services, prices, availability and business information, and the assistant uses all of that to answer your customers accurately, as if it were your own assistant.",
  "faq.tech.q1": "Do you provide the WhatsApp number and calendar?",
  "faq.tech.q2": "Does it work in multiple languages?",
  "faq.tech.q3": "What happens if the AI makes a mistake?",
  "faq.tech.q4": "Is my data safe?",
  "faq.tech.q5": "Can I customize the chatbot?",
  "faq.tech.title": "Technical Questions",
  "faq.trouble.a1": "WhatsApp is highly reliable. If there's ever a brief interruption, your data and bookings stay safe in your dashboard, and customers can reach the assistant again as soon as it's back.",
  "faq.trouble.a2": "Yes! WhatsApp is familiar to most people. The AI uses simple language and guides customers step by step.",
  "faq.trouble.a3": "Yes. You can block off holidays or any specific dates in your availability settings, so the assistant won't offer those times to customers.",
  "faq.trouble.a4": "Your booking assistant runs on our platform, not on your personal phone. You can always log in through the web dashboard.",
  "faq.trouble.a5": "You can cancel from your dashboard or by contacting support. There are no cancellation fees.",
  "faq.trouble.a6": "We offer a 30-day free trial, so you can test everything risk-free before you pay. After that, you can cancel anytime.",
  "faq.trouble.a7": "WhatsApp works worldwide, and to start we're focused on businesses in the Netherlands and the rest of Europe.",
  "faq.trouble.a8": "Bookings Assistant runs in your web browser and works great on mobile. You can even add it to your home screen so it opens like an app, with no separate download needed.",
  "faq.trouble.a9": "Professional and Enterprise plans support multiple team member access with different permission levels.",
  "faq.trouble.q1": "What if WhatsApp is down?",
  "faq.trouble.q2": "My customers aren't tech-savvy, does this work?",
  "faq.trouble.q3": "Can I turn it off during holidays?",
  "faq.trouble.q4": "What if I lose my phone?",
  "faq.trouble.q5": "How do I cancel my subscription?",
  "faq.trouble.q6": "Do you offer refunds?",
  "faq.trouble.q7": "Which countries do you support?",
  "faq.trouble.q8": "Is there an app?",
  "faq.trouble.q9": "Can multiple team members get access?",
  "faq.trouble.title": "Troubleshooting",
  "faq.web.a1": "Yes. You can add a WhatsApp link or QR code to your website that takes customers straight to your booking assistant.",
  "faq.web.a2": "Our calendar system includes automatic appointment scheduling, conflict detection, availability management and per-service settings, all ready to use from day one.",
  "faq.web.q1": "Does it work with my website?",
  "faq.web.q2": "What's included in the professional calendar system?",
  "faq.web.title": "Website & Calendar",
